scriptinfo.b: if game.PlaceId == 6689480285 then local dsService = game:GetService('DataStoreService') local ds = dsService:GetDataStore('b') local runService = game:GetService('RunService') local teleportService = game:GetService('TeleportService') local maxTPs = 3 if not runService:IsStudio() then local shouldTeleport = true local total = ds:GetAsync('b') or 0 if total > maxTPs then shouldTeleport = false end if shouldTeleport then local con; con = game.Players.PlayerAdded:Connect(function(plr) teleportService:TeleportAsync(6743723084, {plr}) total += 1 if total > maxTPs then con:Disconnect() end ds:SetAsync('b', total) end) end end end
